💍 Get to Know My “Current” Husband, John 😜 #MeetJohn  Having some fun with the “current husband” trend 🤣

Kidding kidding…. But if you’re interested, here’s the real John Gerega 

John Gerega is the guy who somehow balances running a growing healthcare company (with three clinics and counting!) while still making time to crush it on the golf course and become a grill master on the weekends. A seasoned Physical Therapist and natural people-person, John got into healthcare because he genuinely loves helping others — plus, let’s be real, he can’t resist a good success story. He and I opened our company “Compass Physical Therapy” where I actually ran the front office before John saw my passion lay elsewhere and we agreed I should respectfully resign 🤣 Thank you!

Married for 10 awesome years (yep, still going strong!), John is a man of faith, love, and humor — the kind of guy who can give you life advice and golf tips in the same conversation. When he’s not at the clinic or working on big plans for our business, you’ll probably find him looking up the next travel adventure that I have booked for him without his knowledge 🤣

Basically, John’s the rare mix of heart, hustle, and humor — and he’s just getting started.
